     H            Y.
     F** UTLR34A  ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : UTILITY- GET DELIVERY# BY PLANT      (FORD)    *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 12/16/2020                                     *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                       *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR34A'
     F*                    PARM           $PLNT   5
     F*                    PARM           $DOCK   4
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $PLNT   5A  PLANT CODE
     F*       $DOCK   4A  DOCK
     F*   OUT $NONY   4A  DELIVERY CODE
     F*       $RTN    1A  RETURN FLAG (BLANK:OK, *:ERROR)
     F****************************************************************
     FABFDP01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     I* SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I*
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80QAEFHZ
     I                                        1   40QAEFYY
     I                                        5   60QAEFMM
     I                                        7   80QAEFDD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $PLNT   5
     C                     PARM           $DOCK   4
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K#PLNT  5
     C                     KFLD           K#DOCK  4
      *
     C                     MOVE '0000'    $NONY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
     C                     MOVEL$PLNT     K#PLNT
     C                     MOVEL$DOCK     K#DOCK
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    S@NONY  4
      *
      * RETRIEVE SYSTEM TIME
     C                     TIME           WSDT
      *
     C           KEY01     SETLLABFDP01
      *
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           KEY01     READEABFDP01                  91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C           QASKJY    ANDNE'D'
     C           QAEFHZ    ANDLETODAY
     C                     MOVELQANONY    S@NONY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      * TRY AGAIN
     C           S@NONY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           K#DOCK    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     MOVEL'00  '    K#DOCK
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN91
     C           KEY01     SETLLABFDP01
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           KEY01     READEABFDP01                  91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C           QASKJY    ANDNE'D'
     C           QAEFHZ    ANDLETODAY
     C                     MOVELQANONY    S@NONY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           S@NONY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELS@NONY    $NONY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
